DOC.brief_summary: This is a retrospective chart review of cases in which the CyPass Micro-Stent was implanted using the Model 241 Applier. The objective of this study is to characterize and evaluate the safety of the Model 241 Applier when used for CyPass Micro-Stent implantation.
DOC.brief_title: Safety and Performance Study of the CyPass System Applier Model 241
DOC.criteria: 1. Diagnosis of OAG 2. CyPass MicroStent implantation (using the CyPass system 241) following uncomplicated phacoemulsification cataract removal and intraocular lens implantation 1. Diagnosis of acute angle closure, traumatic, congenital, malignant, uveitic or neovascular glaucoma 2. Prior incisional glaucoma surgery
